# Short solution needed: "How zip a folder in CLI" (ubuntu) #950

first install zip  and unzip using following command
sudo apt install zip unzip

synatx is:
zip -r filename.zip folder
zip -r filename.zip folder1 folder2
zip -r filename.zip /path/to/folder1 /path/to/file2

for example:
zip -r rithya.zip rithya/